text.tspan: Share of world merchandise trade by type of trade, World
Figure illustrates the share of world merchandise trade by the type of trade. The rich to rich trade series shows the
proportion of merchandise exports that are exported from rich countries to other rich countries as a share of total
Source: CEPII (2016) Two Centuries of Bilateral Trade and Gravity Data: 1827-2014 (2016)
